@startuml
title **Restaurant Ordering Process Flow**

start

:USER places an ORDER\n(Table: ORDER);
note right: Links to **USER** (FK)

:Process **ORDER_ITEM**s;
note right: Links **ORDER** (FK) to **MENU_ITEM** (FK) and records **quantity**

if (All items processed and order is complete?) then (yes)
  :Generate **BILL**\n(Table: BILL);
  note left: Links to **ORDER** (FK) and calculates **total**
  
  :Present Bill and Accept Payment;
  
  stop
else (no)
  :Update ORDER status (e.g., in progress);
  
  stop
endif

@enduml
